      <heading level="2">二、微服务架构设计</heading>
      <heading level="3">2.1 服务拆分策略</heading>
      <heading level="4">拆分原则</heading>
      <paragraph>拆分依据：</paragraph>
      <paragraph>├── 业务边界（高内聚）</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│   ├── 每个服务对应一个完整的业务领域</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│   └── 避免跨领域数据直接依赖</paragraph>
      <paragraph>├── 变更频率（独立部署）</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│   ├── 频繁变更的功能独立拆分</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│   └── 稳定功能可以合并</paragraph>
      <paragraph>├── 团队结构（康威定律）</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│   ├── 每个服务由一个团队负责</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│   └── 2 Pizza Team 原则</paragraph>
      <paragraph>└── 性能隔离</paragraph>
      <paragraph>├── 高性能要求的服务独立部署</paragraph>
      <paragraph>
        └── 避免资源争抢
        <code_block/>
        <code_block/>
      </paragraph>
