      <heading level="3">2.2 服务间通信设计</heading>
      <heading level="4">同步通信（HTTP/gRPC）</heading>
      <paragraph>使用场景：</paragraph>
      <paragraph>├── 用户登录 → 获取用户信息</paragraph>
      <paragraph>├── 创建订单 → 校验用户、校验库存</paragraph>
      <paragraph>├── 支付回调 → 更新订单状态</paragraph>
      <paragraph>└── 查询订单 → 获取订单详情</paragraph>
      <paragraph>通信规范：</paragraph>
      <paragraph>┌────────────────────────────────────────┐</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│            HTTP/gRPC 请求              │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>├────────────────────────────────────────┤</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│ Headers:                               │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│   X-Request-ID: uuid                  │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│   X-Trace-ID: uuid                    │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│   Authorization: Bearer token         │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│   X-From-Service: service-name       │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>├────────────────────────────────────────┤</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│ Body:                                  │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│   {                                    │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│     "method": "getUserInfo",          │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│     "params": { "userId": "xxx" },    │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│     "timestamp": 1234567890          │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│   }                                    │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>
        └────────────────────────────────────────┘
        <code_block/>
        <code_block/>
      </paragraph>
      <heading level="4">异步通信（Kafka）</heading>
      <paragraph>使用场景：</paragraph>
      <paragraph>├── 订单创建 → 触发多系统协同处理</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│   ├── 扣减库存</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│   ├── 发送通知</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│   ├── 更新统计</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│   └── 触发风控</paragraph>
      <paragraph>├── 支付完成 → 通知各相关系统</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│   ├── 订单服务更新状态</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│   ├── 商家收到订单</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│   ├── 骑手接单</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│   └── 财务记账</paragraph>
      <paragraph>└── 用户行为 → 事件采集</paragraph>
      <paragraph>├── 点击事件</paragraph>
      <paragraph>├── 浏览事件</paragraph>
      <paragraph>└── 搜索事件</paragraph>
      <paragraph>Topic 设计：</paragraph>
      <paragraph>┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│ Topic 命名规范: {domain}.{entity}.{action}             │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│                                                         │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│  order.created        # 订单创建                        │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│  order.paid           # 订单支付                        │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│  order.completed      # 订单完成                        │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│  order.cancelled      # 订单取消                        │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│                                                         │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│  payment.succeeded    # 支付成功                        │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│  payment.failed       # 支付失败                        │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│  payment.refunded     # 退款成功                        │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│                                                         │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│  user.registered      # 用户注册                        │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│  user.authenticated   # 用户认证                        │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│                                                         │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│  driver.location      # 司机位置更新                    │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│  rider.location       # 骑手位置更新                    │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│                                                         │</paragraph>
