      <heading level="4">限流策略</heading>
      <paragraph>限流维度：</paragraph>
      <paragraph>├── 按用户限流</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│   ├── 普通用户：100次/分钟</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│   └── VIP用户：500次/分钟</paragraph>
      <paragraph>├── 按IP限流</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│   └── 1000次/分钟</paragraph>
      <paragraph>└── 按接口限流</paragraph>
      <paragraph>├── 下单接口：100次/分钟</paragraph>
      <paragraph>├── 支付接口：50次/分钟</paragraph>
      <paragraph>└── 查询接口：1000次/分钟</paragraph>
      <paragraph>限流算法：</paragraph>
      <paragraph>┌────────────────────────────────────────┐</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│              令牌桶算法                 │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>├────────────────────────────────────────┤</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│                                        │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│    ┌──────┐    令牌    ┌──────────┐   │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│    │Token │ ──────→ │  桶容量   │   │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│    │Bucket│    添加    │ maxTokens │   │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│    └──────┘           └──────────┘   │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│         ↑                              │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│         │                              │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│    请求消费 ←────────── 速率控制         │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│                                        │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│  优点：支持突发流量                     │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│  配置：rate=100, capacity=500          │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│                                        │</paragraph>
