      <heading level="3">3.2 数据分库分表策略</heading>
      <paragraph>分库分表原则：</paragraph>
      <paragraph>├── 按业务拆分</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│   ├── 用户库（user_db）</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│   ├── 订单库（order_db）</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│   ├── 支付库（payment_db）</paragraph>
