      <paragraph>│  3. 写入 Redis                          │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│                                        │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│  Write:                                 │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│  1. 写入 MySQL                          │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│  2. 删除 Redis（延迟双删）               │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│                                        │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>└────────────────────────────────────────┘</paragraph>
